🧠 Important clarification

You’re currently looking in the wrong place for fixing the issue.

👉 The cert must be in two places:

1️⃣ System trust (you already have something here)

/etc/pki/ca-trust/source/anchors/

2️⃣ ❗ CRITICAL (you likely don’t have this)

/etc/containers/certs.d/bastion-sno.lab.ocp.lan:8443/ca.crt

👉 This second one is what actually fixes CRI-O image pulls.


