✅ Do THIS now (don’t explore folders anymore)

🔹 Step 1: Get cert from registry (bastion)

On bastion:

openssl s_client -connect bastion-sno.lab.ocp.lan:8443 -showcerts

Copy the full certificate block:

-----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----
...
-----END CERTIFICATE-----

Save as:

/root/rootCA.pem


