🔹 Step 4: MOST IMPORTANT (don’t skip)

mkdir -p /etc/containers/certs.d/bastion-sno.lab.ocp.lan:8443

cp /etc/pki/ca-trust/source/anchors/rootCA.pem \
   /etc/containers/certs.d/bastion-sno.lab.ocp.lan:8443/ca.crt


